  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Trading electricity if there’s no Brexit deal
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">How cross-border trading and supply of electricity would be affected if there’s a no-deal Brexit.</p>

  </div>
</div>

